  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Twin</strong> rooms are 29m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a bath or shower and a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin </strong>rooms are 31m² and sleep two people. They have a bath or shower and a balcony. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are 45m² and sleep up to four people. There is a double bedroom and bathroom on the entrance level with stairs to a higher balcony room with a double bed and second bathroom. </p>
<p><strong>Double for Sole Use </strong>rooms are 24m² and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
